data.description: Discover this charming home in an established Golf Course Neighborhood in the heart of Bryan! You'll immediately notice the the solid oak double front doors as you enter this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with a semi-open floor plan, connecting the HUGE chef's kitchen to the rest of the home, but with defined space for living, dining, and breakfast nook. Rich finishes like the granite countertops and the wood-look tile, that is as durable as it is beautiful, make this one stand out. Unique to this home is the converted garage flex space—which could easily be a home gym or office, or converted back to a garage, according to your needs. Schedule your personal tour today!
